#X text 746 516 TO TEST: \; IF INSTED OF TBAPLAY~ \, A SINUSOID IS GIVEN (EX: 440[Hz]). THE SPECTRUM OF THIS 440HZ WILL BE 4 BINS OF A DIRICHLET KERNEL. WITH THE SYMMETRY POINT OF DIRICHLET @ 440/(FUNDAMENTAL-FREQUENCY-OF-ANALYSIS). \; FUNDAMENTAL FREQUENCY OF ANALYSIS = SAMPLE-RATE/N = 48000/1024 ~= 46.875 AND SO DIRICHLET CENTERS @ ~9.38. SO IN FILTER \, THE RELEVANT BINS FOR RESYNTHESISZE ARE (8 \, (9 \, 10) \, 11). THERE IS SOME RESIDUALS ANYWAYS UP TO 12 \, 13 AND 7TH BIN. BUT BESIDE THIS BINS ANY OTHER "ACTIVATED" BIN IN THE FILTER WILL RESULT TO "ZERO RESYNTHESIS". \; -IN THE SAME WAY IF YOU ACTIVATE ONLY ONE BIN (EXAMPLE:10TH BIN) OF FILTER \, THEN THERE IS A RANGE OF FREQUENCY INLETS THAT WILL BE RECONSTRUCTED \, FROM (~8)/9 TO 11/(12~). 8 AND 12 ARE EXACTLY ON 0 BUT STILL SOME RESIDUALS. SO IN Hz: FROM 9*46.875 UNTIL 11*46.875 (~421 Hz TO ~516 Hz)., f 75;
